ce:section.ce:para:
Cleaner energy is the future, and the automobile industry is getting there. The government is promoting the use of greener energy on a worldwide scale in an effort to lower pollution levels. In terms of overall pollution, automobiles are the most significant contributor. Cleaner energy in automobiles requires a complete overhaul of the industry. More and more attention is being paid by automotive manufacturers and academic institutions to the development of electric vehicles in an effort to address the challenges that have arisen in the field of electrification [
                     1
                     ]. Implementation of charging station acts as the main challenge for electrification. Hence numerous researchers are working effectively to establish an efficient charging. In [2], the researchers proposed the various design aspects for constructing charging station that includes grid supply, renewable sources and energy storage systems.
